<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:02:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国电池巨头宁德时代拟在香港设立研发中心以支持技术出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-battery-giant-catl-looks-set-up-rd-centres-hong-kong-underpin-technology-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国电池巨头宁德时代董事长周一告诉记者，该公司正在讨论在香港设立研发中心，以创造可在海外和行业内获得许可的新技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-battery-giant-catl-looks-set-up-rd-centres-hong-kong-underpin-technology-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>华友钴业董事长提出电池材料政策化解产能过剩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</link><description>据官方媒体周一报道，浙江华友钴业董事长在中国年度人大会议之前提出，中国应采取措施解决锂电池材料行业产能过剩问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:14:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>克里提升了美国气候声誉，但世界信任仍难以捉摸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-bolstered-us-climate-reputation-though-worlds-trust-still-elusive-2024-03-04/</link><description>周三，约翰·克里准备辞去乔·拜登总统气候变化问题特使的职务，这将使美国在全球气候外交中处于更有利的地位，尽管世界舞台上对美国政策意图的不信任挥之不去。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-bolstered-us-climate-reputation-though-worlds-trust-still-elusive-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园可能会申请法院命令以验证股份转让</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-may-apply-court-order-validate-share-transfer-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国开发商碧桂园周一表示，在评估其离岸重组的进展后，将考虑是否有必要在稍后阶段向高等法院申请生效令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-may-apply-court-order-validate-share-transfer-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>能源部长表示欧盟不能关闭太阳能进口边境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cannot-close-borders-solar-imports-energy-chief-says-2024-03-04/</link><description>欧盟能源政策负责人卡德里·西姆森周一表示，欧盟应该支持陷入困境的欧洲太阳能电池板制造商，但不能对此类产品的进口关闭边境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cannot-close-borders-solar-imports-energy-chief-says-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>解说：本周中国两会的看点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-look-chinas-annual-parliament-session-this-week-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国议会、全国人民代表大会（NPC）将于周二召开年度会议，所有人的目光都集中在支持世界第二大经济体增长的计划上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:54:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-look-chinas-annual-parliament-session-this-week-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>马科斯表示，如果海洋利益被忽视，菲律宾将反击中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾将在有争议的南海问题上与中国合作，但如果其主权和海洋权利被忽视，菲律宾将予以反击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔联盟陷入危机，总理与反对派就新联盟进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-coalition-crisis-pm-talks-with-opposition-new-alliance-2024-03-04/</link><description>尼泊尔总理普什帕·卡迈勒·达哈尔的一名助手表示，周一，他正在与两个反对党进行谈判，以组建新的联盟，理由是与他目前的盟友中间派尼泊尔大会党之间存在困难。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-coalition-crisis-pm-talks-with-opposition-new-alliance-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>对冲基金发现日本可以赚钱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-spot-money-be-made-japan-2024-03-04/</link><description>由于其他主要经济体提高利率以抑制通胀，日本央行长期以来一直处于异类，预计将很快结束其负利率政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-spot-money-be-made-japan-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国自1993年以来首次取消总理新闻发布会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cancels-premiers-press-conference-first-time-since-1993-2024-03-04/</link><description>一名官员周一表示，中国总理李强将不会在今年的年度全国人大会议结束后举行新闻发布会，结束了三十年来的传统。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cancels-premiers-press-conference-first-time-since-1993-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>香港媒体大亨黎智英的国家安全审判：到目前为止发生了什么</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/national-security-trial-hong-kong-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-whats-happened-so-far-2024-03-04/</link><description>香港媒体大亨和民主倡导者黎智英因被指控危害中国国家安全而接受审判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:41:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/national-security-trial-hong-kong-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-whats-happened-so-far-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：迫在眉睫的事件风险无法阻止日经指数突破 40,000 点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-04/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 05:33:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国反对利用反间谍法攻击其营商环境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opposes-using-anti-espionage-law-attack-its-business-environment-2024-03-04/</link><description>全国人大发言人娄勤俭在周一的新闻发布会上对记者表示，中国反对任何通过误读中国反间谍法来诋毁或攻击中国营商环境的行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 05:22:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opposes-using-anti-espionage-law-attack-its-business-environment-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国将于3月5日至11日举行2024年全国人大会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hold-2024-parliamentary-meeting-march-5-11-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国全国人民代表大会发言人娄勤俭在周一的新闻发布会上告诉记者，中国全国人民代表大会（NPC）将于3月5日至11日在北京举行年度会议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:14:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hold-2024-parliamentary-meeting-march-5-11-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪新版畅销电动车价格低于前代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-prices-new-version-best-selling-ev-lower-than-predecessor-2024-03-04/</link><description>随着全球最大汽车市场的价格战愈演愈烈，中国领先的电动汽车 (EV) 制造商比亚迪周一推出了其最畅销汽车的新版本，价格低于其停产前身的最终价格。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 03:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-prices-new-version-best-selling-ev-lower-than-predecessor-2024-03-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>